OL,4,CBristol mayor: Toppling of Colston
OL,5,Cstatue 'not anti-white'
OL,6, The toppling of slaver Edward Colston's
OL,7, statue was "not anti-white", Bristol's
OL,8, mayor has said in a documentary.
OL,10,FStatue Wars: One Summer In Bristol
OL,11,Fdocuments the weeks that followed its
OL,12,Fremoval and shows how Marvin Rees
OL,13,Fmanaged the aftermath.
OL,15,FHistorian David Olusuga helped to
OL,16,Fproduce the film and said it was
OL,17,Fimportant to make it with local people
OL,18,Fwho understood the city's "divisions".
OL,20,FThe documentary airs at 21:00 BST on 10
OL,21,FJune on BBC Two.
